        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_ælǧīn" xml:lang="os-x-iron">
                <form type="lemma"><orth>ælǧīn</orth></form>
                <usg><lang/></usg>
                <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>скупой</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>stingy</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>алчный</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>greedy</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>aftæ ælǧīn ū, æmæ jæ mystytæ dær fælyǧdysty</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>он так скуп, что даже мыши от него разбежались</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>he is so stingy that even the mice fled from him</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ЮОПам."/><biblScope>III
                            190</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно, тот же корень, что в <ref type="xr"
                        target="#entry_ælǧ"/> 'отвращение’ (%iælǧīn%i ‘внушающий отвращение’); ср.
                        <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>argānd, arǧanda</w>
                        <gloss><q>алчный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>жадный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>возбужденный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>гневный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*arγant (ʼrγʼnt)</w>
                        <gloss><q>алчный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>гнусный</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>әrәγant-</w></mentioned>. Конечное %i-in%i может восходить к
                    %i-aina-%i.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">Probably, the same root as in <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ælǧ"
                    /> 'disgust’ (%iælǧīn%i ‘disgusting'); cf. <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>argānd, arǧanda</w>
                        <gloss><q>avid</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>greedy</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>excited</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fa"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>angry</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><lang/>
                        <w>*arγant (ʼrγʼnt)</w>
                        <gloss><q>avid</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="sog"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>vile</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>әrәγant-</w></mentioned>. The final %i-in%i may go back to
                    %i-aina-%i.</etym>
            </entry>
